Initial commit: Ollama CLI v0.1.0

Full-featured AI coding assistant powered by Ollama with multi-provider support.

Features:
- Multi-provider routing (Ollama/Claude/Gemini/Codex)
- Auto-compact context management
- 7 lifecycle hooks mirroring Claude Code
- 3 ANSI status lines (token counter, provider health, dashboard)
- Interactive REPL with 10 slash commands
- Token tracking with cost estimation
- Session persistence and restoration
- GOTCHA Framework + ATLAS Workflow architecture

Built with the ai-code-hooks ecosystem.

